ProjectInfo 
==========================

This project represents the billing genration 


after generating the PDF
we can upload to this into GCP store and get the documentId(UUID)
and publish the object into kafka topic 
from where it will get consumed by other team or process which can make an entry in their data to send the PDF
in the EMAIL or in WHATSAPP as required.



